name: NoName
changelog: Upstreamed to 4.14.325, Disabled many logging, Merged latest WIFI drivers from CLO tag LA.UM.9.1.r1-13900-SMxxx0.QSSI13.0, Merged latest kernel 4.14 CLO tag LA.UM.9.1.r1-13900-SMxxx0.QSSI13.0, Updated KSU to 1027, Other fixes and optimizations related to sched governor, cpu boosting, audio, codecs, camera, ext4 fs, usb and network.
notes: Note: This kernel has kernelSU built in. This kernel also has two editions, RDP ("normal"), Non RDP ("OC" and not "OC" editions too. Continue reading). 66Hz "OC" (Overclock) is a safe value for our display.
